(311, 115, 'panels_data', 'a:3:{s:7:"widgets";a:4:{i:0;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:2659:"<h4><em><strong>Merakee Institute Of Arts.</strong></em></h4>\n<p>Merakee institute Of Arts has established itself as one of the leading institutes in central India in the disciplines of Graphics Designing,Web Designing &amp; Developing Social Media Marketing.Merakee institute Of Arts is characterized by its commitment to educational initiatives where students and professors combine cutting edge technologies with contemporary design and artistic concepts. Preparing students for professional careers, Merakee emphasizes learning through individual attention in a positively oriented institutional environment.We offers professional certificate courses through dedicated faculty, industry exposure, advanced learning resources and comprehensive support services.<strong></strong></p>\n<h4><em><strong>Our USP</strong></em></h4>\n<p>Our experience and knowledge are the core of our plans and strategies, which sets the tone of our approach. We illustrate the compelling stories of our achievements and strengths by inspiring every individual to conquer their dreams and create a presence in the industry. In-depth academic content, project based learning expeditions, case studies, live projects, fieldwork, annual workshops and seminars by industry veterans and top designers, market and industrial visit, innovative classroom learning, international exposure and strong industry connect inspires our students to think global, work as professionals and go beyond classroom learning.</p>\n<h4><em>Our Mission:</em></h4>\n<p>Our sincere efforts are dedicated to impart quality and value based education to raise</p>\n<p>satisfaction level of all the technical aspirants. Our strength is directed to create competent and proactive professionals. Our endeavour is to provide all possible support to promote research and innovative activities.</p>\n<h4><em><strong>Our Vision:</strong></em></h4>\n<p>To achieve best standards standards of quality education by keeping pace with the ever changing technologies and create technical manpower of global standards with</p>\n<p>capabilities of taking on new challenges.</p>\n<h4><em><strong>How to join Merakee Institute Of Arts?</strong></em></h4>\n<p>Career counsellors at <strong>Merakee Institute Of Arts</strong>resolve all your questions on course options in the respective industries,<strong>admission</strong>process, and job placements.</p>\n<p>You can fill in your details<strong>here </strong>or call ?????????????and let us know your requirements, your career plans, etc. Accordingly, Arena''s career counsellors will help you out with your admission process.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong></strong></p>";s:20:"text_selected_editor";s:7:"tinymce";s:5:"autop";b:1;s:12:"_sow_form_id";s:13:"5a819e041ec21";s:19:"_sow_form_timestamp";s:0:"";s:11:"panels_info";a:6:{s:5:"class";s:31:"SiteOrigin_Widget_Editor_Widget";s:4:"grid";i:0;s:4:"cell";i:0;s:2:"id";i:0;s:9:"widget_id";s:36:"a2f622cc-5388-4f4c-a18f-b784438433ae";s:5:"style";a:2:{s:27:"background_image_attachment";b:0;s:18:"background_display";s:4:"tile";}}}i:1;a:7:{s:5:"title";s:6:"Our US";s:4:"text";s:657:"<p>Our experience and knowledge are the core of our plans and strategies, which sets the tone of our approach. We illustrate the compelling stories of our achievements and strengths by inspiring every individual to conquer their dreams and create a presence in the industry. In-depth academic content, project based learning expeditions, case studies, live projects, fieldwork, annual workshops and seminars by industry veterans and top designers, market and industrial visit, innovative classroom learning, international exposure and strong industry connect inspires our students to think global, work as professionals and go beyond classroom learning.</p>";s:20:"text_selected_editor";s:4:"html";s:5:"autop";b:1;s:12:"_sow_form_id";s:13:"5a819e5b06133";s:19:"_sow_form_timestamp